{"tid":1491980,"cid":33,"subCid":0,"title":"［國際文宣請入］知唔知黑警而家做嘅嘢同蘇聯思想警察冇分別啊！","createTime":"2019-08-20T15:37:34.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-20T20:14:37.000Z","uid":236917,"like":8,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"3d4ec33f6ed40eb0fc0d163b168503755d1f90ee","tid":1491980,"uid":236917,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-20T15:37:34.000Z","msg":"首先解釋吓<br />\n1973年，索忍尼辛寫嘅《古拉格群島》，講述由被拘捕到入勞動營一連串恐怖嘅經歷，當中<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">不乏俾當時NKVD/NKGB拘留時嘅對待</span></span><br />\n一時轟動全球，更加攞咗諾貝爾文學獎<br />\n時至今日，如Jordan Peterson等外國知名學者都仍然有積極討論呢本書，知名度同影響力係20世紀算係數一數二<br />\n加上KGB係世界（尤其東歐國家）係臭名昭著，因為同蓋世太保嘅惡行絕對有得比，同佢地掛勾通常都冇好結果<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n第三章-盤問 以列點形式講咗31種極權政府下秘密警察盤問方式<br />\n當中包括：<br />\n1.夜晚盤問<br />\n2.遊說<br />\n3.言語侮辱<br />\n4.Good cop Bad cop<br />\n<br />\n以上都係比較輕微，接下落黎到重頭戲<br />\n5.羞辱（畫家、天水圍女義士）<br />\n6.係盤問過程令人困惑、感到騷擾<br />\n7.恐嚇（前途、刑期等）<br />\n8.講大話<br />\n9.恐嚇（拉屋企人、朋友）<br />\n10.躁音滋擾<br />\n12.用煙頭lat人<br />\n13.強光滋擾<br />\n14.阻止休息<br />\n15.好細、生活環境極差嘅羈留室<br />\n18.罰跪<br />\n19.罰企<br />\n20.唔俾飲水<br />\n21.唔俾訓覺<br />\n22.嘗試幾日都要求被捕人唔訓集中精神<br />\n24.Punishment cell<br />\n26.唔俾食嘢<br />\n27.無傷痕嘅毆打<br />\n28.打斷指甲腳甲<br />\n29.阻止移動（如拘束衣）<br />\n30.毆打/打斷骨、脊椎<br />\n<br />\n係咪同最近大家見到/聽到嘅嘢好相似？<br />\n冇錯，因為黑警嘅做法已經有25項中咗啦<br />\n即係話佢地同蘇共對政治嫌疑犯已經冇咩大分別<br />\n求外國文宣多強調 煲撚大佢<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/aura.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/aura.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/aura.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ad1c72777444fac106ff80af27b8b395427a04f1","tid":1491980,"uid":236917,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-20T15:40:38.000Z","msg":"Push<br />\n612 721 811"},{"pid":"288c74120d78bc553b9c9d62c5b99ce1cda6426d","tid":1491980,"uid":203417,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-20T15:41:39.000Z","msg":"文宣做野啦，加油"},{"pid":"83ebbc0868fcb8e5087a1e0df1f684cebcf5a201","tid":1491980,"uid":2562,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-20T15:42:32.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/PXcMrux.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FPXcMrux.jpg&h=54112853&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/PN4V4gd.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FPN4V4gd.jpg&h=bf41982c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2019/08/20/233941_35db8952adc66a9b8fad2b475503a348.jpeg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2019%2F08%2F20%2F233941_35db8952adc66a9b8fad2b475503a348.jpeg&h=ba2d15e1&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/0y2D12U.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F0y2D12U.jpg&h=c7bab806&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/pYuV4gf.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FpYuV4gf.jpg&h=52b2bc94&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/tri4dee.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Ftri4dee.png&h=7af3e96e&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"8783a79e0997baae3c6817efa6fe9dad4e09dd4f","tid":1491980,"uid":249243,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-20T15:44:25.000Z","msg":"721"},{"pid":"7f9920ff0f7ff9c0da8a90710cd1dca81e66b836","tid":1491980,"uid":236917,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-20T15:46:15.000Z","msg":"Push"},{"pid":"24f450c01d7fdaa2527b11cefa2aef4ae6cea870","tid":1491980,"uid":264051,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-20T15:53:13.000Z","msg":"點解咁多首歌唔用，支那帝吧徧要用咁撚重納粹色彩既歌？ 當左自己係SS黨衞軍？？？ <br />\n[鍵戰] 煲大佢! 支那帝吧=中國新納粹<br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1491871\" data-auto-link target=\"_blan